                     <interp inst="t17890909-100-verdict502" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder5s"></interp>
               GUILTY, 1 s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17890909-100-punish503" type="punishmentDescription">
